snippet.textDisplay: Kinda feel like the three kisses story is weird if you don’t understand Dutch tradition. When you greet acquaintances, friends, family etc you give each other three kisses hello and good bye on the cheek. So they were saying good bye. Nikki would have three kisses everyone. If you like each other  but are not officially dating you normally linger a bit or kiss closer to the mouth (like demonstrated in the video). If you don’t like someone you do the opposite. It’s a very telling practice haha
snippet.textOriginal: Kinda feel like the three kisses story is weird if you don’t understand Dutch tradition.
